{"type":null,"faqId":12177,"title":"Y600-U00 WLAN待机的时候会自动断开，怎么解决，手机默认是什么设置？","answer":"<p>\n\t<span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">这个问题是休眠策略的问题。进入的方法：在主屏幕，点击<img alt=\"\" src=\"http://consumer.huawei.com/support/servlet/imageServlet?dlType=HtmlAreaImage&amp;imageId=33603\" /></span><span><span>&gt; </span></span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">设置</span><span><span> &gt; </span></span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">无线和网络</span><span><span> &gt; WLAN</span></span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">，再点击菜单键<img alt=\"\" src=\"http://consumer.huawei.com/support/servlet/imageServlet?dlType=HtmlAreaImage&amp;imageId=33604\" /></span><span><span> </span></span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">并进入高级</span><span><span> &gt; </span></span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">在休眠状态下保持</span><span><span>WLAN</span></span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">连接，设置为“始终”。</span></span> \n</p>\n<p>\n\t<span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">注：手机默认设置是始终，也就是一直可以正常连接。如果调整休眠策略就会使得在待机时自动断开。</span><span><span>3</span></span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">个选项的含义如下：</span></span> \n</p>\n<p>\n\t<span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">始终：一直保持</span><span><span>WLAN</span></span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">的连接。</span></span> \n</p>\n<p>\n\t<span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">仅限充电时：只有在充电时才一直保持连接，如果不充电，待机后</span><span><span>3</span></span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">分钟断开连接。</span></span> \n</p>\n<p>\n\t<span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">从不（会增加数据网络流量）：待机后</span><span><span>3</span></span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">分钟断开连接。</span></span> \n</p>","faqTypeId":138,"faqType":"网络与数据共享","useful":0,"unUseful":0,"languageId":2,"languageName":"zh_cn","faqCode":"2984","faqTypeCode":"Handsets-Network-Data-sharing","isTop":"0","moduleCode":"faq","productId":null,"productCode":null,"postDate":1399185923000,"seriesProductName":"Y600-U00","visitedTimes":68,"isUsefulFlag":null,"score":0,"times":0,"imageList":null,"displayType":"text","justView":"0","fileName":null,"filePath":null,"imagePath":null,"imageName":n